This file includes changes since the last upload. It is intended to provide a reference for translators/authors/remastering.

-------------- v 0.7 ----------------
* Important! layout and structure changes (XSL&XML) as follows: 17/9/2003
-- removed "edited with free software" section as this is now automatically generated
-- old document/language tags are obsolete, now using <article lang="hebrew"|"arabic"|"russian"|"english"> 16/9/2003
-- main body tags now have to be encapsulated within <main></main>
-- old segment tags (subtitle, subtitle2, subtitle3) are obsolete and replaced with (chapter, section, subsect)
-- new tag <toc/> to generate table of content
-- <chapter> now adds an index number. New tag <chapnotoc> doesn't add number and exclude from TOC
* New explanation file 'MANUAL' for developing swimming guide articles. 17/9/03
* new guide: apps_list.xml

-------------- v 0.6 ----------------
