* change: man_enigma >> man_games and updated 22/8/03
* some typo corrections: tour_kinneret.xml, user_interface.xml,first_time.xml, desktop_ready/xml 2/9/03
* Important! wide impact due to removal of quotes (") from filenames where ever <IMAGE> tag was used 12/9/03

